CREATE TABLE `isb-cgc.GDC_metadata.rel18_aliquot2caseIDmap`
(
  program_name STRING OPTIONS(description="Program name, eg TCGA or TARGET"),
  project_id STRING OPTIONS(description="ID of the Project -- e.g. TCGA-BRCA, TARGET-AML, etc."),
  case_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="GDC unique identifier"),
  case_barcode STRING OPTIONS(description="Submitter identifier, eg HCC1954, TCGA-ZX-AA5X, etc"),
  sample_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Unique GDC identifier for this sample (corresponds to the sample_barcode), eg a1ec9279-c1a6-4e58-97ed-9ec1f36187c5  --  this can be used to access more information from the GDC data portal"),
  sample_barcode STRING OPTIONS(description="Original/submitter sample ID"),
  sample_type STRING OPTIONS(description="Two-digit sample_type code which forms part of the sample barcode eg. 01,11,06, etc."),
  sample_type_name STRING OPTIONS(description="The longer name of the sample type; eg. Primary Tumor, Recurrent Tumor, etc."),
  sample_is_ffpe STRING OPTIONS(description="Whether a smaple is FFPE, either  False,  None ,  True, or null"),
  sample_preservation_method STRING OPTIONS(description="Sample Preservation Method, usually null or  FFPE, also Snap Frozen or Frozen"),
  portion_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Portion GDC ID"),
  portion_barcode STRING OPTIONS(description="Original/submitter portion ID"),
  analyte_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Analyte GDC ID"),
  analyte_barcode STRING OPTIONS(description="Original/submitter analyte ID"),
  aliquot_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Unique GDC identifier for this aliquot (corresponds to the aliquot_barcode), eg 7fbfdb3e-1fd2-4206-8d2e-7f68e4a15844  --  this can be used to access more information from the GDC data portal"),
  aliquot_barcode STRING OPTIONS(description="Original TCGA aliquot barcode, eg TCGA-12-1089-01A-01D-0517-01")
)
OPTIONS(
  friendly_name="ALIQUOT IDS TO CASE IDS REL18",
  description="Data was generated from file metadata information from the GDC release 18, downloaded July 12, 2019. Aliquot barcodes are mapped to case information.\nMore details: https://docs.gdc.cancer.gov/Data/Release_Notes/Data_Release_Notes/#data-release-180",
  labels=[("access", "open"), ("data_type", "file_metadata"), ("source", "gdc"), ("status", "archived"), ("category", "metadata")]
);

CREATE TABLE `isb-cgc.GDC_metadata.rel13_caseData`
(

  project__program__name STRING OPTIONS(description="Program Name"),
  project__project_id STRING OPTIONS(description="Program Short Name with Project Short Name"),
  submitter_id STRING OPTIONS(description="This can be used to identify a corresponding entry in the submitter's records. The GDC requires that submitter_id be unique for each entity within a project: the tuple (combination) of [ project_id, submitter_id ] is a unique key."),
  legacy_file_count INT64 OPTIONS(description="Total number of files for this case in the GDC legacy archive"),
  active_file_count INT64 OPTIONS(description="Active Archive File Count")
)
OPTIONS(
  friendly_name="CASE DATA REL13",
  description="Data was generated from file metadata information from the GDC legacy archive release 13, October 2018. More details: https://docs.gdc.cancer.gov/Data/Release_Notes/Data_Release_Notes/#data-release-130",
  labels=[("access", "open"), ("data_type", "file_metadata"), ("source", "gdc"), ("status", "archived"), ("category", "metadata")]
);

  case_gdc_id STRING OPTIONS(description="GDC unique identifier"),
  project_dbgap_accession_number STRING OPTIONS(description="Program dbGaP accession number, eg phs000188"),
  project_disease_type STRING OPTIONS(description="The type of disease studied by the project; eg. Sarcoma,  Breast Invasive Carcinoma,Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia, etc"),
  project_name STRING OPTIONS(description="Project Name; frequently the same as or similar to the project disease type eg   Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia - Phase II   or   Breast Invasive Carcinoma   etc"),
  program_dbgap_accession_number STRING OPTIONS(description="Program dbGaP accession number, eg phs000178"),
  program_name STRING OPTIONS(description="Program name, eg TCGA or TARGET"),

  downstream_analyses__workflow_link STRING OPTIONS(description="Name of GDC workflow, eg VarScan2 Annotation (if applicable, NULL where no information is available)"),
  downstream_analyses__workflow_type STRING OPTIONS(description="Name of GDC workflow, eg VarScan2 Annotation (if applicable, NULL where no information is available)"),
  experimental_strategy STRING OPTIONS(description="Experimental strategy used to generate data (where applicable) e.g. WXS, RNA-Seq"),
  file_name STRING OPTIONS(description="Name of file at the GDC"),
  file_size INT64 OPTIONS(description="The size of the file measured in bytes"),
  file_id STRING OPTIONS(description="GDC file identifier. This is a duplicate of file_gdc_id field found in some tables. "),

  platform STRING OPTIONS(description="Platform used to generate this data, eg  Illumina  , or  Affymetrix SNP 6.10"),

)
